{"title":"时刻记在心","authors":["许钦堂"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":1,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"时刻记在心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘夸公社比天好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿当时刻记在心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改变贫困千斤担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社帮咱挑八百斤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能舍命不能舍公社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握紧枪杆保卫幸福根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘金口玉言说的好："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全凭咱毛主席好领导。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天大、地大、都不大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都没有咱毛主席伟大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命红旗举得高握得牢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨上长途迎着东风飘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们红心交给毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举起枪来宣誓："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远听党的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远听毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟人民走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远做驯服的工具。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驻南京部队　许钦堂"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}